- **Proposed layout** — 8 organized zones: Quick Stats Bar, Band & Skill Progression Chart, Skill Breakdown Cards, Study Activity Chart, Vocabulary Retention & Growth, Mistake Trends, Study Plan Adherence, Recent Activity Feed
