- **Empty, loading, error states** — progressive hydration from cached snapshot, skeleton patterns per chart type, retry/fallback behavior
- **Mobile layout** — 2-column stat cards, stacked chart sections, collapsed period selector, proper touch targets
- **AI Tutor integration** — header review button, contextual "Ask AI" per section, insight cards, proactive tutor messages
- **18 components needed** — references existing components (`ProgressChart`, `StatCard`, `TrendBadge`) and proposes new ones (`BandProgressionChart`, `SkillBreakdownGrid`, `VocabRetentionChart`, `PeriodSelector`)
- **Design notes** — band ladder metaphor, streak flame chain, radar chart for skill balance, vocabulary garden metaphor, celebration micro-interactions
